{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji49.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于党组织的指示","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于党组织的指示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年3月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们总要有一个党，现在这样的状况是一种暂时现象，没有一个党是不行的。各个革命造反派的组织怎么能代替党？革命委员会也不能代替党。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":3}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":389,"page_end":389},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}